OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe night
OL,6,Fwill continue cloudy and mild with
OL,7,Ffurther outbreaks of rain, this heavy
OL,8,Fat times particularly over the hills.
OL,9,FStrong to gale southerly winds along
OL,10,Fthe coast, easing in the early hours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FOvernight rain clearing away
OL,13,Fin morning. Then the rest of the day
OL,14,Fwill be largely dry with bright or
OL,15,Fsunny intervals. Showery rain
OL,16,Fspreading to Argyll and the Isles
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
